statements: SELECT * FROM fish_species;
SELECT species_name, growth_rate FROM fish_species WHERE feeding_schedule = 'Twice daily';
SELECT species_name, feeding_schedule FROM fish_species ORDER BY growth_rate DESC;
SELECT breeding_habits FROM fish_species WHERE species_id = 3;
SELECT * FROM fish_species WHERE growth_rate > 0.5;
SELECT species_id, species_name FROM fish_species WHERE growth_rate > 0.5 ORDER BY species_name DESC;
SELECT * FROM fish_species WHERE breeding_habits LIKE '%livebearers%' ORDER BY species_name ASC;
SELECT species_name, feeding_schedule FROM fish_species WHERE growth_rate BETWEEN 0.3 AND 0.7 ORDER BY feeding_schedule;
SELECT species_name, breeding_habits FROM fish_species WHERE breeding_habits IS NOT NULL ORDER BY species_name;
SELECT * FROM fish_species WHERE growth_rate < 0.4 AND feeding_schedule LIKE '%twice%' ORDER BY growth_rate DESC;
SELECT * FROM FishSpecies;
SELECT species_name, growth_rate FROM FishSpecies;
SELECT feeding_schedule FROM FishSpecies WHERE species_name = 'Salmon';
SELECT species_name, feeding_frequency FROM FishSpecies JOIN AquacultureManagement ON FishSpecies.species_id = AquacultureManagement.species_id;
SELECT species_id, species_name, breeding_habits FROM FishSpecies ORDER BY species_id DESC;
SELECT * FROM FishSpecies WHERE growth_rate > 0.5 ORDER BY species_name ASC;
SELECT species_name, feeding_schedule FROM FishSpecies WHERE species_id = 3;
SELECT species_name, feeding_schedule FROM FishSpecies WHERE feeding_schedule LIKE '%twice%' AND breeding_habits IS NOT NULL;
SELECT * FROM AquacultureManagement WHERE feeding_frequency = 'daily' AND temperature_range BETWEEN '25' AND '30';
SELECT s.species_name, m.feeding_frequency FROM FishSpecies s JOIN AquacultureManagement m ON s.species_id = m.species_id;

SELECT species_name, growth_rate, feeding_schedule FROM FishSpecies;

SELECT species_id, species_name, growth_rate FROM FishSpecies WHERE growth_rate > 0.5;
SELECT species_id, breeding_description FROM BreedingHabits WHERE breeding_id IN (1, 3, 5);
SELECT * FROM FishSpecies WHERE species_name='Goldfish';
SELECT species_name, growth_rate FROM FishSpecies WHERE growth_rate > 0.5 ORDER BY species_name ASC;
SELECT species_name, feeding_schedule FROM FishSpecies WHERE feeding_schedule LIKE '%twice a day%' ORDER BY species_name DESC;

SELECT species_name, breeding_description FROM FishSpecies JOIN BreedingHabits ON FishSpecies.species_id = BreedingHabits.species_id WHERE BreedingHabits.breeding_description IS NOT NULL ORDER BY species_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM GrowthRates WHERE growth_rate < 0.3 ORDER BY species_id ASC;
SELECT * FROM FishSpecies;
SELECT species_name, growth_rate FROM FishSpecies WHERE growth_rate > 0.5;
SELECT species_name FROM FishSpecies WHERE feeding_schedule IS NOT NULL ORDER BY species_name DESC;
SELECT * FROM GrowthRates INNER JOIN FishSpecies ON GrowthRates.species_id = FishSpecies.species_id;
SELECT species_name, feeding_schedule FROM FishSpecies JOIN FeedingSchedules ON FishSpecies.species_id = FeedingSchedules.species_id;
SELECT * FROM FishSpecies WHERE species_name = 'Goldfish';
SELECT species_id, species_name, growth_rate FROM FishSpecies WHERE growth_rate > 0.5 ORDER BY growth_rate DESC;
SELECT species_name, feeding_schedule FROM FishSpecies JOIN FeedingSchedules ON FishSpecies.species_id = FeedingSchedules.species_id WHERE feeding_schedule LIKE '%twice a day%';
SELECT species_name, breeding_habits FROM FishSpecies JOIN BreedingHabits ON FishSpecies.species_id = BreedingHabits.species_id WHERE breeding_habits IS NOT NULL ORDER BY species_name ASC;

SELECT f.species_name, g.growth_rate, h.breeding_habits, s.feeding_schedule FROM FishSpecies f LEFT JOIN GrowthRates g ON f.species_id = g.species_id LEFT JOIN FeedingSchedules s ON f.species_id = s.species_id LEFT JOIN BreedingHabits h ON f.species_id = h.species_id WHERE g.growth_rate >= 0.5 AND s.feeding_schedule NOT LIKE '%weekend%' ORDER BY f.species_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM FishSpecies;
SELECT species_name, growth_rate FROM FishSpecies WHERE growth_rate > 2.5;
SELECT species_name, feeding_schedule FROM FishSpecies WHERE feeding_schedule LIKE '%Twice a day%';
SELECT * FROM TankDetails WHERE water_ph < 7.0 ORDER BY tank_size DESC;
SELECT * FROM FeedingRecords WHERE feeding_quantity BETWEEN 50 AND 100 ORDER BY feeding_date ASC;
SELECT * FROM FishSpecies ORDER BY species_name DESC;
SELECT species_name, growth_rate, breeding_habits FROM FishSpecies WHERE growth_rate > 3.00;
SELECT t.tank_id, t.tank_size, tr.feeding_quantity, tr.feeding_date FROM TankDetails t JOIN FeedingRecords tr ON t.tank_id = tr.species_id;
SELECT f.species_name, b.breeding_date, b.offspring_quantity FROM FishSpecies f JOIN BreedingRecords b ON f.species_id = b.species_id WHERE b.offspring_quantity >= 10 ORDER BY b.breeding_date DESC;

SELECT TOP 5 t.tank_id, t.tank_location, f.species_name, tr.feeding_quantity, tr.feeding_date FROM TankDetails t JOIN TankOccupancy to ON t.tank_id = to.tank_id JOIN FishSpecies f ON to.species_id = f.species_id JOIN FeedingRecords tr ON f.species_id = tr.species_id ORDER BY tr.feeding_date ASC;
